t.showMessage?topicID=3043.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showMessage?topicID=3106.topic"> Next Topic >> </a> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95% cellpadding=5 cellspacing=1><tr><td valign=top  class=headings><font color=#333399>Author</font></td><td valign=top  class=headings><font color=#333399>Comment</font></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uelurinashwood.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Elurin Ashwood</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/5/01 5:27:59 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Gladiator Armor</span><hr size=1> Just wondering if anyone can confirm gladiator armor dropping off the two spawned Gladiators in the arena of Kael (get a ticket, hand to Vkjor, and 2 gladiators spawn). Want to try to get gladiator sleeves and leggings solo if possible since everyone I ever hunt with is on giant faction.<br>
<br>
-Elurin Ashwood <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umacnat.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Macnat</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://hem1.passagen.se/lonnelid/english.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/6/01 12:11:48 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Gladiator Armor</span><hr size=1> Gladiator armour drops off 2 named mobs near the arena. I forget the names, but they take a couple of groups to kill. <p><br>
<P><a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=61605">Macnat</a><BR>
Hierophant
<br> 
The Nameless
<br>

</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usplendora.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Splendora</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/6/01 10:03:48 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Gladiator Armor</span><hr size=1> Vealok the Angry drops sleeves and Bjorak the Cold<br>
drops legs. When you drop into the arena, facing the<br>
two doors at the back, Bjorak is behind the left door<br>
and Vealok behing the right. When you pull them you will<br>
also get a gladiator with each of them. Respawn is random and quite slow, chances are if you stay for 3 hours or so<br>
you will only get one pair of each, but you can at least<br>
get them right away as soon as you get into the arena. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uaerillea.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aerillea</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/9/01 12:03:08 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Gladiator Armor</span><hr size=1> Hehe- just a little fashion info, the only tunic I've found that will match the glad arms and legs to form that perfect gladiator look is the fungi tunic =p <p>Aerillea

Chere Amie of Team HLS</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ucarathosollathir.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Carathos Ollathir</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/globalRainbow.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/9/01 1:16:26 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Gladiator Armor</span><hr size=1> Yeah, got some arms the other day and looks like regular banded.  booooooo <p><a href=http://www.afflictionguild.com/scripts/member.x?username=Carathos&charactername=Carathos>Carathos Ollathir<BR><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bthedruidsgrove> 59th Druid<BR> <a href=http://www.afflictionguild.com/>~Affliction~<BR>
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utauronoftunare.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tauron of Tunare</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/11/01 1:54:22 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> how rare are they?</span><hr size=1> How rare are they? My guild went to arena for a shot time and we killed Bvorek the Cold twice and Vealok the Angry once and no arms or legs =( Do they drop ONLY from those two? Thanks =)<br>
<br>
Tauron <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ujambone.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jambone</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/11/01 9:12:41 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: how rare are they?</span><hr size=1> Every time we have killed Vealok and Bjorek they have dropped the pants and arms.  I have never seen arms or legs drop from the gladiators that spawn with these two, though I have heard of it happening.  What I am curious about is whether the named pair have a rare drop.  Anyone ever seen them drop anything but the chain arms and legs? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usplendora.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Splendora</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/11/01 10:11:30 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: how rare are they?</span><hr size=1> Yep...Bjorak the Cold can drop a monk weapon and<br>
Vealok the Angry can drop a pretty crappy sword.<br>
<br>
The armor seems to be the common drop though. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utauronoftunare.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tauron of Tunare</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/19/01 1:53:52 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> not happening</span><hr size=1> My guild has killed vealok twice and the other named twice as well and I have yet to see a piece of gladiator armor drop =( We even pulled them to the arena as opposed to just fighting them in the small corridor to see if that could be a factor /shrug - still no arms or pants.<br>
<br>
So either gladiator armor is actually not common and you guys were just extremely lucky or they changed the armor to rare a couple of weeks ago.<br>
<br>
Anyone has some fresh info on this please? Thanks =)<br>
<br>
Tauron <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/urandomuser.showPublicProfile?language=EN>random user</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/19/01 3:40:38 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: not happening</span><hr size=1> Did they drop nothing at all, or the other thing that they sometimes drop?<br>
<br>
I don't know too much myself, but we're about to go check it out... will let you know if I find out anything.<br>
<br>
Also, in theory if you fight the two of them in that corridor, do you get adds?<br>
<br>
- Xylem, E'ci <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utauronoftunare.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tauron of Tunare</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/19/01 4:29:15 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> gladiator</span><hr size=1> They dropped some sword and monk weapon I think - no gladiator armor. My best guess it that its not a common drop after all. I suggest you pull him to the arena. Both nameds will come with a gladiator. Be careful thou because pathing there is so bad the nameds might run inside and come back with a protector of zek (a pull of 3). If he comes with just a gladiator bodyguard you can take them with 2 groups easy.<br>
<br>
Please let me know if you got anything and all the detalis involved. Thanks<br>
<br>
Tauron <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umacnat.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Macnat</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://hem1.passagen.se/lonnelid/english.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/20/01 5:16:16 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: gladiator</span><hr size=1> Unless the drop table has changed, gladiator armour was the common drop, I know Remedy have got about 10 pairs of each and for us it droped almost every time. <p><br>
<P><a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=61605">Macnat</a><BR>
Hierophant
<br> 
The Nameless
<br>

</p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showMessage?topicID=3043.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showMessage?topicID=3106.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.emailToFriend?topicID=3079.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.threadControl?topicID=3079.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/gfx/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3079.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3079.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub13.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thedruidsgrovegeneral">General - EQ<option value="thedruidsgrovefrm27">General - DAOC<option value="thedruidsgrovegeneralot">General - OT<option value="thedruidsgrovefrm18">FAQ & Index<option value="thedruidsgrovefrm20">Spoilers<option value="thedruidsgrovespells">Spells<option value="thedruidsgrovequests">Quests<option value="thedruidsgrovedruidicequipment">Druidic Equipment<option value="thedruidsgrovehuntingguide">Hunting Guide<option 